 />\n勁到癲 無負「禿哨」之名<br />\n<br />\n再睇埋個名<br />\nKarim Mostafa Benzema<br />\nKylian-lotin MBappe<br />\n兩個法國光頭十號仔KMB<br />\n兩個人真係好似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"你條對曼聯球皇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禁都叫神級表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麥巴比係摩納哥對曼城既表現都屌打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391039e41d204e8f88a65b7e90394661a6f781f2","tid":2411484,"uid":199081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qHKPlo-vP2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqHKPlo-vP2s&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN29HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=23cbd689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qHKPlo-vP2s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ju508U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ju508U.jpg&h=d660cfe5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d9552cd9feec1377230e083c5dee75633bdb6e6","tid":2411484,"uid":239205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"你老4勁過賓施馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9482594652a9c480cdfbec5042df9f481c03bb9a","tid":2411484,"uid":73381,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"賓施馬<br />\n因為踢法 技術 能力有如施丹與朗拿度的混合體<br />\n所以有「禿哨」嘅稱號<br />\n成名作應該係曼聯對里昂嗰場<br />\n喺領隊經過摩佬 肥安 肥賓 拖一 盧柏迪利 蘇拿利 拖二時期<br />\n競爭對手有希古恩 小豆 莫拉達 祖域 馬里安奴嘅情況下<br />\n佢依然喺皇馬企足十年正選<br />\n而家係歐聯史上第五射手<br />\n亦係皇馬史上第四射手<br />\n入多球就會過埋傳奇迪史堤芬奴做第三<br />\n唯獨埋門未到一線頭<br />\n但盤扭傳送滯空穩定性球商樣樣都有<br />\n非常全能嘅射手<br />\n一直為C朗做綠葉 拉邊hold波 禁區拉扯<br />\n令C朗可以完全發揮禁區殺手嘅本色<br />\n兩者之間亦都有好多onetwo彈彈波互相助攻入波<br />\n毫無疑問係C朗嘅最佳拍擋同將C朗推上頂峯嘅男人<br />\n到近年C朗走咗<br />\n身邊由C朗變咗雲尼素斯 阿辛斯奧 經常傷嘅巴爾<br />\n賓施馬就獨力承擔緊皇馬嘅入球重責<br />\n喺拖二時期更加好高嘅自由度<br />\n經常拉邊持球組織<br />\n同摩迪一左一右做皇馬嘅前場核心<br />\n亦都令卻奧斯有更大空間後上/遠射<br />\n而最癲嘅係<br />\n賓施馬喺近年嘅Big Games係永遠冇甩拖<br />\n一直穩定維持極高水平"},{"pid":"d60fd5a2c0264b617480ad939c31d9d113d25f9d","tid":2411484,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3qEwyh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3qEwyh.jpg&h=d2aac046&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KiK6byh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKiK6byh.gif&h=b0b9a156&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONM4HE0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONM4HE0.gif&h=c6f0376d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxmMbyn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxmMbyn.jpg&h=8dd2b15e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvBPTMK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvBPTMK.gif&h=d035c21c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6SLr6M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6SLr6M.gif&h=a8338330&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PreaDdr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPreaDdr.gif&h=98cf84bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/heoF0rM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FheoF0rM.jpg&h=99e3d208&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aecb712eee246cb685939d54bf95a2f25c047c01","tid":2411484,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9482594652a9c480cdfbec5042df9f481c03bb9a","tid":2411484,"uid":73381,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"賓施馬<br />\n因為踢法 技術 能力有如施丹與朗拿度的混合體<br />\n所以有「禿哨」嘅稱號<br />\n成名作應該係曼聯對里昂嗰場<br />\n喺領隊經過摩佬 肥安 肥賓 拖一 盧柏迪利 蘇拿利 拖二時期<br />\n競爭對手有希